{"about_the_game":"Wake up in the medieval fantasy world of <strong>Podnabu</strong>! You are the guardian of a magical sword. Fight against hordes of skeletons and monsters. Solve mysteries and become a real hero!<br>Many wanderers have fallen into the tangled secrets of this world, remaining in the dark even after death. But perhaps it is you who can uncover the true essence of this world.<br>Explore mysterious dungeons and a flying city, unravel ancient secrets and become a true hero! Ready to take on the challenge? Go on to adventure and glory!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881770/extras/gifFIN1.gif?t=1722316947\" /><br><strong>In the marvellous RPG world awaits you :</strong><br>-Photorealistic environment <br>-Open world <br>-Customisation of your weapons<br>-Old, abandoned castles<br>-Deep caves with various riddles and mysteries<br>-NPCs with unique dialogues<br>-Epic battles with various mobs <br>-Non linear plot <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881770/extras/gifFIN2.gif?t=1722316947\" /><br><strong></strong><br>-The story, full of unexpected twists and turns and deep characters, will not leave you indifferent.<br>-Sound accompaniment complements the picture, immersing you in the atmosphere of what is happening. <br>-Gameplay offers plenty of opportunities to explore and interact with the world.<br>-Enjoy stunning views and detailed locations that will make you believe in the reality of this fantastic world.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"1 LVL","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2881770/2b634e491c1d26ff03047f983b3f429ad5ed693e.jpg"},{"name":"Hi Fox","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2881770/1e0126e983043529a0ad9ac2c4e014d899206628.jpg"},{"name":"Ancient bridge","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/imag